.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  fisherman, librarian, software-developer, mechanic, chef
There are 5 different nationalities: english, spanish, ukranian, norwegian, japanese
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, zinnia, begonia, tulip, marigold
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, milk, orange-juice, water
5 different pets are kept: dog, fox, zebra, horse, snails

1. the english is the fisherman
2. the spanish is the owner of the dog
3. the person drinking coffee is the librarian
4. the ukranian is the person drinking tea
5. the librarian is to the right of the software-developer
6. the person who growsamaryllis is the owner of the snails
7. the person who growszinnia is the mechanic
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the owner of the fox
11. the person who growszinnia is to the left or right of the owner of the horse
12. the person who growstulip is the person drinking orange-juice
13. the japanese is the person who growsmarigold
14. the norwegian is to the left or right of the chef

.:: Answer ::.
